          <font>
            <Font name="System Bold" size="18.0" />
          </font>
        </Label>
            <Label alignment="CENTER" contentDisplay="CENTER" layoutX="32.0" layoutY="98.0" prefHeight="175.0" prefWidth="619.0" text="This program is designed to show usage, behaviour and interactions of Java Threads. It is designed to be a graphical presentation and beside starting by pressing 'Start' button it does not require any particular user actions. Close all by cliking 'Reset' at the end. 'Threads' is using Java Concurrency, implementation of 'Runnable' interface, inheritance of 'Task' observable class as well as  threads sleep, join, interrupt and more." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" textFill="#111111" wrapText="true">
